and was happy.

15:03.203 --> 15:04.903
And he walked through the world

15:04.905 --> 15:07.405
carrying the tiny candle
of hope,

15:07.407 --> 15:11.109
shielding it against the
bitter winds of negativity.

15:11.111 --> 15:14.279
