16:27.153 --> 16:28.753
Damn, I was hoping for up.

16:28.755 --> 16:33.124
Wow, sounds like you're
a really hands-on manager.

16:33.126 --> 16:35.159
Hold on. Could you
come back later?

16:35.161 --> 16:37.996
I'm on a business call.

16:37.998 --> 16:40.598
I bet you're in
the donkey business,

16:40.600 --> 16:43.501
because you seem
like a real ass man.

16:43.503 --> 16:45.169
Hey! Get the hell
out of here!

16:45.171 --> 16:46.537
Damn it, Donna!
She's losing him!

16:46.539 --> 16:48.673
Guess he likes 'em pimply.

16:48.675 --> 16:50.675
Gals, we're going in!

16:50.677 --> 16:53.945
Hi, here I am.
Another maid.

16:53.947 --> 16:55.513
I've got what you want,

16:55.515 --> 16:58.116
and I'm about to give you
what you need.

16:58.717 --> 17:00.151
Wait. It's you!

17:00.153 --> 17:01.552
You're sick!

17:01.554 --> 17:03.054
Am I?
Am I sick?!

17:03.056 --> 17:05.323
