women and butts everywhere!

17:40.060 --> 17:41.325
Well, all you've done

17:41.327 --> 17:43.027
is out-creep
a serial ass-grabber.

17:43.029 --> 17:44.495
You're fired!

17:44.497 --> 17:46.998
