to juvie!

18:21.468 --> 18:23.234
Those 'mos will take away
my blades!

18:23.236 --> 18:26.737
Then you all have four hours
to learn this song.

18:26.739 --> 18:27.872
You're gonna convince

18:27.874 --> 18:30.108
