the senior citizens
were clubbed to death?

18:45.925 --> 18:49.060
No, it's the one
that had e coli in
the swimming pool.

18:49.062 --> 18:51.996
Now I'm glad you got that
negativity out of your system,

18:51.998 --> 18:55.233
